	<project_license>GPL-3.0-only</project_license>

	<description>
		<p>COSMIC Web Apps written with love and libcosmic.
			Allow you to simply create web applications from given URL working inside separate window of your browser of choice.
			Works on most mainstream desktop environments with all the mainstream web browsers installed via flatpak.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Fast and easay to use</li>
			<li>Works out of the box</li>
			<li>In-app icon pack installer</li>
			<li>Supports most mainsteam browsers</li>
		</ul>
	</description>

